public class ShippingDroplet
extends DynamoServlet

This droplet is used to inform the fulfillment system that a given shipping group has shipped. It takes the following parameters orderId - The id of the order containing the shipped group. shippingGroupId - The id of the shipping group that just shipped. The output is one of two values "ShipCallSucceeded" or "ShipCallFailed"
